"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/424484","HM Treasury","false","2015-11-05","<p>HM Revenue and Customs does not hold easily accessible data regarding the number of requests made for paper copies of tax returns forms in the last 12 months.</p>","South West Hertfordshire","Mr David Gauke",,"2015-11-05T16:31:49.713Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/424484/answer","Biography information for Mr David Gauke","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/424484/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/424484/answer",,,,,"14","Treasury","CaTreasury","2015-10-28","Taxation: Self-assessment","1","House of Commons","To ask Mr Chancellor of the Exchequer, how many requests have been made for paper copies of tax return forms in the last 12 months.","false","Biography information for Joanna Cherry","Edinburgh South West","Joanna  Cherry","13960"
